\label{sec:design}
% ============================================================================

\subsection{Architecture Overview}

CleanTest-Agent follows a \textbf{pipeline-of-skills} architecture, where each processing stage is encapsulated as an independent Agent Skill. Figure~\ref{fig:architecture} illustrates the overall system design.

\begin{figure}[h]
\centering
